cruited women who suffered from chronic yeast For the first months the women each day ate ounces of yogurt containing Lactobacillus For the second months the women did not eat The researchers examined the women each month and found that incidents of colonization and infection were significantly lower during the period when the women ate The fungus Candida albicans can live in the body without doing It is an overproliferation of the fungus that leads to The researchers concluded that the acidophilus bacteria found in some brands of yogurt retard overgrowth of the Streptococcus thermophilus and bulgaricus are the two bacteria most commonly used in commercial yogurt Neither one appears to exert a protective effect against Candida albicans Women who want to try yogurt as a preventive measure should choose a brand that lists acidophilus in its end InfoTrac Health Reference Center Oct ' Oct ' THE MATERIAL CONTAINED IN Health Reference Center Oct ' Oct ' IS PROVIDED ONLY FOR INFORMATIONAL PURPOSES AND SHOULD NOT BE CONSTRUED AS MEDICAL ADVICE OR CONSULT YOUR HEALTH PROFESSIONAL FOR ADVICE RELATING TO A MEDICAL PROBLEM OR Heading CANDIDA ALBICANS Candida Monilia Infections Caused by Fungi Infectious Diseases by Harold Neu The Columbia of Physicians Surgeons Complete Home Medical Guide Edition ' TEXT AVAILABLE TEXT COPYRIGHT Crown Publishers Candida Monilia This disease is usually caused by Candida albicans a fungus that we all carry at one time or In some circumstances though the organisms proliferate producing symptomatic infection of the mouth intestines vagina or When the mouth or vagina are infected the disease is commonly called Vaginitis caused by Candida often afflicts women on birth control pills or There is itching and a white cheesy Among narcotic addicts Candida infections can lead to heart valve Diagnosis of Candida infections is confirmed by cultures and blood Treatment can be with amphotericin B or orally with There is no evidence that Candida in the intestine